race.comment: FAST FELIX (5) looks close to another win after finishing second last time (22.90) in a Maiden at Murray Bridge. His last run is a proven strong form reference. Can find winning form. POP'S GIRL (1) failed to threaten on debut finishing sixth (20.22) at this track over 340m. Gets the coveted rails draw for the first time. Much improved and rates a winning chance. WHITEWOOD (2) copped a check in the run and finished a well held 11 lengths fifth (20.19) last time in a Grade 6 at this track over 340m. Should be in this for a long way. YES EILEEN (6) was unplaced here last start but gets her chance to atone.
